@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="text-muted text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container">
    <p class="lead text-justify">Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website.</p>

    <h2 class="text-uppercase text-muted mb-4">Information we collect</h2>
    <p class="text-justify">We only collect information about you if we have a reason to do so - for example, to provide our services, to communicate with you, or to make our services better.</p>
    <p class="text-justify">We collect this information from three sources: if and when you provide information to us, automatically through operating our services, and from outside sources.</p>
    <p class="text-justify font-italic">We may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul class="list-group mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item">Contact information, such as your name, email address, mailing address, and phone number</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Payment information, such as your credit card number or bank account information</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Order information, such as the items you purchase, shipping address, and order history</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Device and usage information, such as your IP address, browser type, and operating system</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-uppercase text-muted mb-4">How we use your information</h2>
    <p class="text-justify">We use the information we collect to provide our services to you, to communicate with you, to improve our services, and to personalize your experience.</p>

    <h2 class="text-uppercase text-muted mb-4">Security</h2>
    <p class="text-justify">We take reasonable measures to help protect information about you from loss, theft, misuse, and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.</p>

    <h2 class="text-uppercase text-muted mb-4">Changes to our Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-justify">We may change this privacy policy from time to time. We will post any privacy policy changes on this page and, if the changes are significant, we will provide a more prominent notice.</p>

    <h2 class="text-uppercase text-muted mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-justify">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item">Email: info@yourshop.com</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Phone: 555-1234</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">Address: 123 Main St, Anytown, USA</li>
    </ul>
</div>
